-- Nordex Chief Sees `Surge' in Orders From U.S. Next Year, Handesblatt Says
-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 2010-09-21T05:22:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/nordex-chief-sees-surge-in-orders-from-u-s-next-year-handesblatt-says.html
Nordex SE  expects a “surge” in
U.S. orders for next year due to a government promotional
program,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing Chief Executive Officer
 Thomas Richterich .  Nordex is three-quarters of the way toward its sales
targets for the current year, the newspaper quoted Richterich as
saying in an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
 nkresge@bloomberg.net  